{"title":"NCL(The NCAR Command Language)Linux,Windows多平台安装","uid":"a1a8603ea3ed2b561af50bfd8a1ae45f","slug":"NCL","date":"2019-11-30T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2019-11-30T16:00:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/NCL.json","keywords":"Linux, LaTeX, Blog","cover":"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/03.png","content":"<h1 id=\"NCL-The-NCAR-Command-Language-Linux-Windows多平台安装\"><a href=\"#NCL-The-NCAR-Command-Language-Linux-Windows多平台安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"NCL(The NCAR Command Language)Linux,Windows多平台安装\"></a>NCL(The NCAR Command Language)Linux,Windows多平台安装</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>NCL(The NCAR Command Language)是一种专门为科学数据处理以及数据可视化设计的高级语言，很适合用在气象数据的处理和可视化上。–百度百科</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/NCLMainImage_logos.png\" alt=\"logo\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Linux下安装\"><a href=\"#Linux下安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Linux下安装\"></a>Linux下安装</h2><p>NCL官网：<a href=\"http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/\">http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/</a><br>进入到下载页面</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/01.png\" alt=\"01\"></p>\n<p>ncl的官网提供了3种安装方式</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p><code>conda</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>二进制安装包</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>源码编译安装</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/02.png\" alt=\"02\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-Conda方式安装NCL\"><a href=\"#1-Conda方式安装NCL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.Conda方式安装NCL\"></a>1.Conda方式安装NCL</h3><h4 id=\"Conda简介\"><a href=\"#Conda简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Conda简介\"></a>Conda简介</h4><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Conda 是一个开源的软件包管理系统和环境管理系统，用于安装多个版本的软件包及其依赖关系，并在它们之间轻松切换。 Conda 是为 Python 程序创建的，适用于 Linux，OS X 和Windows，也可以打包和分发其他软件。</p></blockquote>\n<p>Conda的安装详见下面这个文章</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>作者：卖萌哥<br>链接：<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/edaa744ea47d\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/edaa744ea47d</a></p></blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"安装ncl\"><a href=\"#安装ncl\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装ncl\"></a>安装ncl</h4><p>如果您已有conda，但已有一段时间未更新，则可能需要通过从UNIX终端窗口键入以下内容来更新它：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">conda update -n root --all</code></pre>\n\n<p>然后安装<code>ncl-stable</code>软件包</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">conda create -n ncl_stable -c conda-forge ncl\nsource activate ncl_stable</code></pre>\n\n<p>安装完成！</p>\n<p>输入如下代码，检测安装结果：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">ncl -V\nng4ex xy05n -clean -W png</code></pre>\n\n<p>显示如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/03.png\" alt=\"03\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-二进制包安装\"><a href=\"#2-二进制包安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.二进制包安装\"></a>2.二进制包安装</h3><p>在下载页面中</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/04.png\" alt=\"04\"></p>\n<p>点击里面的<code>a list of binaries</code>链接。进入到二进制安装包的下载页面</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/05.png\"></p>\n<p>在下载页面，提供了多个Linux平台的下载链接，比如常见的CentOS、Debian等，你根据自己使用的平台来选择。网站在国外，下载会很慢，请耐心等待。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>如果不介意版本新旧的话，可以在我分享的百度网盘链接下载：</p>\n<p>链接: <a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1wjMWLIdpPgUNmBt5O8RjHQ\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1wjMWLIdpPgUNmBt5O8RjHQ</a>  密码: 3bi6</p>\n<p>如果链接挂掉，请务必邮件告知我。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>因为NCL是图形化编程，因此必须在Linux的图形桌面下安装。</p>\n<p>打开终端</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo mkdir &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ncl-6.4.0 #以我分享的ncl版本为例\nsudo tar -xvf ～&#x2F;ncl_ncarg-6.4.0-CentOS7.3_64bit_gnu485.tar.gz -C &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ncl-6.4.0\n#假设你的ncl包在用户目录下</code></pre>\n\n<p>如果第一次执行的时候报错，提示缺少libgfortran.so.3这个库文件，我们来安装这个包。命令是：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">yum install libgfortran -y #以CentOS为例，其他平台类似，具体请自行百度</code></pre>\n\n<p>如果有其他问题，请查阅<a href=\"http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/linux.shtml\">http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/linux.shtml</a></p>\n<p>为了更方便使用，我们将ncl的路径添加到系统路径中去</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">vim ~&#x2F;.bashrc</code></pre>\n\n<p>在结尾添加如下</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">export NCARG_ROOT&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ncl-6.4.0\nexport PATH&#x3D;$NCARG_ROOT&#x2F;bin:$PATH</code></pre>\n\n<p>然后保存退出（:wq）。（vim是一款极其著名的命令行编辑器，其操作使用方法可以百度一下）</p>\n<p>然后执行命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">source ~&#x2F;.bashrc</code></pre>\n\n<p>测试一下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">ncl -V</code></pre>\n\n<p>如果能正确显示NCL的版本号，说明安装完毕且正确。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-源码编译安装\"><a href=\"#3-源码编译安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.源码编译安装\"></a>3.源码编译安装</h3><p>略略略，有时间再更新^_^</p>\n<h2 id=\"Windows下安装\"><a href=\"#Windows下安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Windows下安装\"></a>Windows下安装</h2><h3 id=\"在Windows下安装Ubuntu子系统\"><a href=\"#在Windows下安装Ubuntu子系统\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在Windows下安装Ubuntu子系统\"></a>在Windows下安装Ubuntu子系统</h3><h4 id=\"安装-Windows-10-的-Linux-子系统组件\"><a href=\"#安装-Windows-10-的-Linux-子系统组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 Windows 10 的 Linux 子系统组件\"></a>安装 Windows 10 的 Linux 子系统组件</h4><p>顺序： -&gt; 系统设置 -&gt; 应用 -&gt; 右侧的程序和功能 -&gt; 启动或关闭windows功能 -&gt; 勾选适用于 Linux 的 Windows 子系统</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/06.jpg\" alt=\"06\"></p>\n<p>确定后，重启电脑，系统更新配置。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>重启后，打开 Windows 应用市场，输入 linux 搜索，选择你自己想要的系统版本，选择 Ubuntu</p>\n<p>然后点击启动，第一次会进行初始化安装。</p>\n<p>初始化安装完成，设置帐号密码，用户名我们直接使用 root ，然后设置下密码就搞定了（在Linux下输入密码是不会显示*的）</p>\n<p>windows 的 CMD 不好用，推荐个很不错的替代软件 <code>Cmder</code> 。下载地址：<a href=\"http://cmder.net/\">http://cmder.net/</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"Ubuntu基础配置\"><a href=\"#Ubuntu基础配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Ubuntu基础配置\"></a>Ubuntu基础配置</h4><p>更换国内数据源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo cp &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;sources.list &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;sources.list.backup\nsudo vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;sources.list</code></pre>\n\n<p>在vim中，按<code>i</code>进入输入模式</p>\n<p>我们使用清华的源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"># 默认注释了源码镜像以提高 apt update 速度，如有需要可自行取消注释\ndeb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic main restricted universe multiverse\ndeb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse\ndeb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse\ndeb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse\n\n\n# 预发布软件源，不建议启用\n# deb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</code></pre>\n\n<p>将以上全复制进<code>sources.list</code>，按<code>Esc</code>退出到命令模式，保存退出（<code>:wq</code>）</p>\n<p>然后更新</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo apt-get update</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"安装附加软件包\"><a href=\"#安装附加软件包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装附加软件包\"></a><span id=\"jump-01\">安装附加软件包</span></h4><p>接下来，我们需要安装一些ncl可能需要的包</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo apt-get install csh libfontconfig gfortran libgfortran3\nsudo apt-get install libxrender-dev libx11-dev libxrender1\nsudo apt-get install libssh2-1 libgomp1\nsudo apt-get install firefox imagemagick</code></pre>\n\n<p>NCL需要图形界面，我们需要安装<code>Xming</code>来显示图形。<code>Xming</code>的下载链接 <a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/xming/\">https://sourceforge.net/projects/xming/</a></p>\n<p>有时候Xming会出现问题，尽量在启动Ubuntu之前先启动Xming。</p>\n<p>如果你觉得Xming无法满足你，你可以参考这篇文章：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u011138447/article/details/78262369\">https://blog.csdn.net/u011138447/article/details/78262369</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"下载NCL\"><a href=\"#下载NCL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载NCL\"></a>下载NCL</h4><p>你可以直接用命令下载到Ubuntu</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.earthsystemgrid.org&#x2F;download&#x2F;fileDownload.html?logicalFileId&#x3D;246ab3ec-fa02-11e6-a976-00c0f03d5b7c</code></pre>\n\n<p>或者，在<code>/mnt/</code>有c、d……之类的目录，其对应Windows的C盘、D盘…… 所以你可以将你之前下载好的包拷贝到Ubuntu的当前工作目录。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo mkdir &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ncl-6.6.2 #以6.6.2为例\nsudo tar -zxf ~&#x2F;ncl_ncarg-6.6.2-Debian7.11_64bit_gnu472.tar.gz -C &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ncl-6.6.2\n#假设你的ncl包在你的用户目录下</code></pre>\n\n<p>然后</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">vim ~&#x2F;.bashrc</code></pre>\n\n<p>在vim中，按<code>i</code>进入输入模式，在最后添加</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">export NCARG_ROOT&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ncl-6.6.2\nexport PATH&#x3D;$NCARG_ROOT&#x2F;bin:$PATH\nexport DISPLAY&#x3D;:0</code></pre>\n\n<p>按<code>Esc</code>退出到命令模式，保存退出（<code>:wq</code>）。</p>\n<h4 id=\"测试你的NCL\"><a href=\"#测试你的NCL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试你的NCL\"></a>测试你的NCL</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">ncl -V</code></pre>\n\n<p>如果输入ncl版本，例如“6.4.2”，说明安装成功。</p>\n<p>或者可以</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">cp $NCARG_ROOT&#x2F;lib&#x2F;ncarg&#x2F;nclex&#x2F;xyplot&#x2F;xy04n.ncl .\nncl xy04n.ncl</code></pre>\n\n<p>会输出一张图表</p>\n<h4 id=\"一些可能的问题\"><a href=\"#一些可能的问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一些可能的问题\"></a>一些可能的问题</h4><p>如果出显了一些错误，比如告诉你缺少了”lib<em>xxxx</em>.so”这类的库，你可以用”sudo apt-get install xxxx”来安装缺少的库或者包。</p>\n<p>如果你看到了这样的错误：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">warning:GKS:GOPWK: --X driver error: error opening display</code></pre>\n\n<p>这可能是你没有设置DISPLAY的环境变量，或者设置错误，输入</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">printenv DISPLAY</code></pre>\n\n<p>详情请看这篇文章：<a href=\"http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/windows_linux_subsystem.shtml#SetDisplay\">http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/windows_linux_subsystem.shtml#SetDisplay</a></p>\n<p>如果你的问题还没有解决，也可以参考这篇文章：<a href=\"https://wenku.baidu.com/view/a5f722906e1aff00bed5b9f3f90f76c660374c61.html\">https://wenku.baidu.com/view/a5f722906e1aff00bed5b9f3f90f76c660374c61.html</a> window10下Linux子系统 + NCL 安装记录</p>\n<h3 id=\"虚拟机下安装Ubuntu来运行ncl\"><a href=\"#虚拟机下安装Ubuntu来运行ncl\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"虚拟机下安装Ubuntu来运行ncl\"></a>虚拟机下安装Ubuntu来运行ncl</h3><p>在Windows下有两款常用的虚拟机软件，VMware和Oracle VM VirtualBox，其中VMware是付费软件，Oracle VM VirtualBox是一款多平台的开源免费软件。<br>VMware附许可码：链接: <a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1eAApTcS-J-JY4MSApsHXcQ\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1eAApTcS-J-JY4MSApsHXcQ</a>  密码: 25ut<br>Oracle VM VirtualBox的官网下载链接： <a href=\"https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads\">https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads</a></p>\n<p>我们还需要Ubuntu系统镜像文件，考虑到国内的网络环境，我们选择在清华大学的开源软件镜像站下载：<a href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu-releases/eoan/ubuntu-19.10-desktop-amd64.iso\">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu-releases/eoan/ubuntu-19.10-desktop-amd64.iso</a></p>\n<p>你也可以在这 <a href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/#\">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/#</a> 找到最新版</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/qinghua.png\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"Oracle-VM-VirtualBox\"><a href=\"#Oracle-VM-VirtualBox\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Oracle VM VirtualBox\"></a>Oracle VM VirtualBox</h4><p>我这里使用Oracle VM VirtualBox来介绍一下安装</p>\n<p>装好Oracle VM VirtualBox后</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/14.png\"></p>\n<p>新建</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/15.png\"></p>\n<p>尽量不要把安装文件夹放在C盘</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/16.png\"></p>\n<p>剩下的一路默认到底</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/17.png\"></p>\n<p>然后点启动：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/21.png\"></p>\n<p>这时候会弹出一个对话窗，然后可以选择我下好的Ubuntu系统镜像</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/22.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/23.png\"></p>\n<p>然后选择中文</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/24.png\"></p>\n<p>安装Ubuntu</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/25.png\"></p>\n<p>如果网路状况不好，可以不选择“安装Ubuntu时下载更新”</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/27.png\"></p>\n<p>然后</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/28.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/NCL_File/29.png\"></p>\n<p>之后输入个人信息：用户名，口令等。单击“继续”，安装过程可能需要几十分钟，请耐心等待。</p>\n<h4 id=\"配置\"><a href=\"#配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置\"></a>配置</h4><p>启动Ubuntu，打开终端窗口</p>\n<p>一个要点是：命令，文件名要通过<code>Tab</code>补全，这样就会减少录入错误。</p>\n<p>介于国内网络环境，我们先把数据源更换为清华的开源软件镜像站</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo cp &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;sources.list &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;sources.list.backup\nsudo vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;sources.list</code></pre>\n\n<p>在vim中，按<code>i</code>进入输入模式（如果提示没有安装vim，可以使用<code>nano</code>来编辑，可以参考这篇文章：<a href=\"https://man.linuxde.net/nano%EF%BC%89\">https://man.linuxde.net/nano）</a></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"># 默认注释了源码镜像以提高 apt update 速度，如有需要可自行取消注释\ndeb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic main restricted universe multiverse\ndeb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse\ndeb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse\ndeb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse\n# deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;ubuntu&#x2F; bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse</code></pre>\n\n<p>按Esc退出到命令模式，保存退出（:wq）。</p>\n<p>通过</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo apt-get update;sudo apt-get upgrade</code></pre>\n\n<p>来更新一下系统</p>\n<p>然后可以参考前面的  <a href=\"#jump-01\">跳转</a> 来完成配置和ncl安装。</p>\n<h3 id=\"Cygwin下运行ncl\"><a href=\"#Cygwin下运行ncl\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Cygwin下运行ncl\"></a>Cygwin下运行ncl</h3><p>可以参考这个：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/Vicky510475733/article/details/79101561\">https://blog.csdn.net/Vicky510475733/article/details/79101561</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\"><a href=\"#参考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考\"></a>参考</h2><p>Installing NCL with “conda” <a href=\"http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/conda.shtml\">http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/conda.shtml</a></p>\n<p>NCL在Linux安装教程 <a href=\"https://jingyan.baidu.com/article/ab69b2707beaea2ca7189ffc.html\">https://jingyan.baidu.com/article/ab69b2707beaea2ca7189ffc.html</a></p>\n<p>conda的安装与使用 <a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/edaa744ea47d\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/edaa744ea47d</a></p>\n<p>告别NCL 拥抱Python <a href=\"https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1471168\">https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1471168</a></p>\n<p>NCL 6.5.0 在Ubuntu 16.04下的安装 <a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/ce680e7ec8ed\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/ce680e7ec8ed</a></p>\n<p>Running NCL under Linux systems <a href=\"http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/linux.shtml\">http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/linux.shtml</a></p>\n<p>Installing and running NCL on Windows 10 Linux Bash shell <a href=\"http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/windows_linux_subsystem.shtml\">http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/windows_linux_subsystem.shtml</a></p>\n<p>Windows10安装Linux子系统Ubuntu <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zhouzme/article/details/78780479\">https://blog.csdn.net/zhouzme/article/details/78780479</a></p>\n<p>Windows 10’s Bash shell can run graphical Linux applications with this trick <a href=\"https://www.pcworld.com/article/3055403/windows-10s-bash-shell-can-run-graphical-linux-applications-with-this-trick.html\">https://www.pcworld.com/article/3055403/windows-10s-bash-shell-can-run-graphical-linux-applications-with-this-trick.html</a></p>\n<p>How to Install and Use the Linux Bash Shell on Windows 10 <a href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/249966/how-to-install-and-use-the-linux-bash-shell-on-windows-10/\">https://www.howtogeek.com/249966/how-to-install-and-use-the-linux-bash-shell-on-windows-10/</a></p>\n<p>windows 10中的ubuntu子系统安装桌面环境的方法（How to install Ubuntu-desktop in windows 10 Subsystem for Linux） <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u011138447/article/details/78262369\">https://blog.csdn.net/u011138447/article/details/78262369</a></p>\n<p>window10下Linux子系统 + NCL 安装记录 <a href=\"https://wenku.baidu.com/view/a5f722906e1aff00bed5b9f3f90f76c660374c61.html\">https://wenku.baidu.com/view/a5f722906e1aff00bed5b9f3f90f76c660374c61.html</a></p>\n<p>Set DISPLAY environment variable <a href=\"http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/windows_linux_subsystem.shtml#SetDisplay\">http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/windows_linux_subsystem.shtml#SetDisplay</a></p>\n<p>nano命令 <a href=\"https://man.linuxde.net/nano\">https://man.linuxde.net/nano</a></p>\n<p>新手进行Cygwin/X(Windows)系统下安装使用NCL <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/Vicky510475733/article/details/79101561\">https://blog.csdn.net/Vicky510475733/article/details/79101561</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"其他\"><a href=\"#其他\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"其他\"></a>其他</h2><h3 id=\"告别NCL-拥抱Python\"><a href=\"#告别NCL-拥抱Python\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"告别NCL 拥抱Python\"></a>告别NCL 拥抱Python</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>晴天一声雷，NCL官网发布重要通告，他们决定不再更新NCL转而向Python发展。WHAT???我刚把NCL用熟了你就跟我说这个。</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>但做出这种选择确实也是有一定道理的，python在地球科学社区中的应用越来越广泛，很多优秀的团队还有大牛基于python开发出了不少地球科学相关的库。得益于这些优秀的库，近些年python在地球科学领域快速发展，并逐渐成为未来的趋势。现在python不但可以替代NCL而且还能提供很多NCL不具备的功能。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"NCL-to-Python\"><a href=\"#NCL-to-Python\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"NCL to Python\"></a>NCL to Python</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>NCL的功能在python中转为了PyNIO和PyNGL这两个库：<br>1.PyNIO使用了NetCDF的接口用来读写各种类型的数据，包括NetCDF、GRIB、HDF等。<br>2.PyNGL是一个可视化的库，里面的参数设置和NCL中的很相似。</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>其实让大家从一门自己熟悉的语言转换到另一门语言的过程是很痛苦的，前期肯定是特别的不习惯，但只要熬过了短暂的过渡期后面很快就能适应过来。不过幸运的是NCL团队很贴心的给出了NCL向Python过渡的指导手册（NCL-to-Python Transition Guide），链接在文末。熟悉NCL的小伙伴借助官方的文档一定能很快的完成向python的过渡。</p></blockquote>\n<p>NCL-to-Python Transition Guide (PDF) <a href=\"http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Document/Manuals/NCL_to_Python/Transition_Guide_NCL_PyNGL.pdf\">http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Document/Manuals/NCL_to_Python/Transition_Guide_NCL_PyNGL.pdf</a></p>\n","text":"NCL(The NCAR Command Language)Linux,Windows多平台安装 NCL(The NCAR Command Language)是一种专门为科学数据处理以及数据可视化设计的高级语言，很适合用在气象数据的处理和可视化上。–百度百科 Linux下安装NC...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"9.5k","symbolsTime":"9 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":1,"path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"n